WEBVTT

00:53.928 --> 00:55.972
The last moments of my parent's lives...

00:57.891 --> 00:59.434
were ruined by me.

01:01.061 --> 01:02.771
When they saw me run off,

01:04.397 --> 01:05.732
they were disappointed in me.

01:06.816 --> 01:07.734
Where are you going?

01:07.901 --> 01:09.319
<i>With that, their lives...</i>

01:09.486 --> 01:10.779
Do you even have money?

01:10.862 --> 01:12.363
<i>...came to a sudden end.</i>

01:14.407 --> 01:15.825
I made it that way.

01:17.202 --> 01:18.244
I doubt that.

01:20.497 --> 01:23.833
In their last moments,
they must've thought "What a relief.

01:24.709 --> 01:26.920
What a relief that our son got off."

01:28.588 --> 01:29.881
That's what they thought.

01:34.969 --> 01:36.971
I would be living just fine.

01:38.598 --> 01:39.891
And then out of nowhere...

01:41.059 --> 01:42.894
I would remember that day.

01:44.562 --> 01:45.939
And I hated myself.

01:50.944 --> 01:53.905
I started Happiness to lessen my guilt.

01:55.573 --> 01:57.075
It was my parents' life wish...

01:58.993 --> 02:00.995
to expand Happiness.

02:08.962 --> 02:11.673
I started it because of my guilt.

02:12.924 --> 02:18.596
I didn't want to pretend
to be a good andÂ kind person.

02:20.056 --> 02:21.349
I understand everything.

02:23.476 --> 02:24.727
But it wasn't your fault.

02:28.314 --> 02:29.315
It was my fault.

02:30.150 --> 02:31.693
It wasn't your fault.

02:34.654 --> 02:35.864
It was my fault.

02:37.365 --> 02:38.575
You're a victim too.

02:39.909 --> 02:41.327
You lost your family.

02:46.207 --> 02:48.710
You just did something a little immature.

02:49.210 --> 02:51.546
An accident happened to occur
at that moment.

02:53.798 --> 02:55.049
You're a victim.

02:57.510 --> 03:00.722
Let's stop talking about this.

03:10.607 --> 03:11.566
Sorry.

03:13.776 --> 03:15.528
I made you bring up your painful past.

03:18.781 --> 03:19.782
Song Ma-rin.

03:21.701 --> 03:26.122
So far, this is all that I can tell you.

03:29.083 --> 03:29.918
I...

03:33.546 --> 03:35.381
do have secrets from you.

03:37.133 --> 03:38.301
After the accident...

03:40.136 --> 03:42.263
something unbelievable happened.

03:45.058 --> 03:45.934
For now,

03:46.976 --> 03:49.103
it's just not something I can tell you.

03:51.231 --> 03:54.234
Can you accept that
and wait a little longer?

03:56.110 --> 03:57.278
Until when?

04:02.033 --> 04:03.034
I don't know.

04:04.953 --> 04:07.914
March 25, 2019?

04:09.207 --> 04:10.124
What?

04:12.835 --> 04:13.878
There will be...

04:15.630 --> 04:17.632
<i>a fireworks festival that night.</i>

04:19.384 --> 04:21.552
<i>Let's go see that together.</i>

04:23.137 --> 04:25.139
<i>We'll watch fireworks all night.</i>

04:26.516 --> 04:27.725
<i>After that...</i>

04:31.104 --> 04:35.108
I will tell you
everything that happened to me.

04:37.193 --> 04:38.611
This thing you can't tell me...

04:40.071 --> 04:42.490
it's not something I should worry about,
is it?

04:46.661 --> 04:50.665
Unlike the accident at Namyeong Station,

04:52.250 --> 04:54.502
I'm going to make sure
I don't have any regrets.

04:55.795 --> 04:58.506
So trust me.

05:02.802 --> 05:04.679
That's a long way off.

05:08.016 --> 05:09.392
When is it again?

05:10.601 --> 05:12.020
2019.

05:13.688 --> 05:14.814
March 25.

05:23.614 --> 05:25.116
We'll be going now.

05:25.575 --> 05:26.951
-Thank you.
-Thank you.

05:28.453 --> 05:31.539
I rested well for a few days.

05:31.706 --> 05:33.791
You must think this is a resort.

05:34.292 --> 05:35.752
We're not going home yet.

05:35.835 --> 05:37.003
We're going somewhere?

05:37.295 --> 05:38.296
That place.

05:38.755 --> 05:39.589
Where?

05:40.256 --> 05:41.132
That place.

05:53.353 --> 05:55.146
What are you doing for so long?

05:57.148 --> 05:58.441
I made a wish.

05:59.192 --> 06:00.610
For things to go well for you.

06:00.735 --> 06:02.153
Are they God or something?

06:04.655 --> 06:07.075
I said sorry for not knowing
who they were earlier.

06:07.909 --> 06:10.495
I'm trying to make it fun,
so that you don't feel sad.

06:10.745 --> 06:12.038
Can't you play along?

06:16.042 --> 06:18.378
"I'll be good to So-joon forever."

06:19.295 --> 06:22.048
Isn't it the kind of thing you say
to your in-laws?

06:23.716 --> 06:25.009
You wish!

06:25.385 --> 06:26.594
What about this then?

06:29.013 --> 06:31.599
"I won't ever be sick enough
to go to the hospital again.

06:32.433 --> 06:36.521
I'll make sure
your son doesn't have to worry."

06:41.776 --> 06:43.945
Why bother expecting anything from you?

07:14.434 --> 07:15.768
Wow.

07:15.852 --> 07:18.146
Home really is the best.

07:20.064 --> 07:21.649
It's so nice.

07:46.466 --> 07:47.467
What?

07:48.092 --> 07:50.845
Nothing. I feel strange.

07:53.139 --> 07:57.143
You know how people say
they feel like they've been born again?

07:58.811 --> 08:02.190
It feels like you and I have been reborn.

08:04.484 --> 08:06.736
I feel like things will work out,
whatever we do.

08:07.737 --> 08:09.197
Only good things will happen.

08:10.156 --> 08:11.866
That's just how I'm feeling.

08:13.075 --> 08:14.076
It's nice.

08:17.914 --> 08:19.207
I'll do better for you.

08:20.833 --> 08:23.461
Thank you for saying that.

08:26.589 --> 08:30.384
Then... I won't be using
that small room anymore.

08:31.636 --> 08:32.512
Of course not.

08:32.929 --> 08:35.223
Use our bedroom. I'll use the small room.

08:35.848 --> 08:36.724
What?

08:36.807 --> 08:39.393
<i>You want to keep using separate rooms?</i>

08:39.685 --> 08:42.563
How can I feel at ease
if you sleep in the small room?

08:43.397 --> 08:44.732
Use our room.

08:46.150 --> 08:49.028
<i>Why are you being like this?</i>
<i>Didn't we make up?</i>

08:50.530 --> 08:53.824
Just because I told you more about myself,

08:54.700 --> 08:58.412
I'm not assuming
you're over everything that upset you.

08:58.996 --> 09:02.208
Women aren't as simple as men.

09:02.291 --> 09:03.876
How different could they be?

09:04.377 --> 09:06.587
Two arms and two legs.

09:06.754 --> 09:09.465
-Do you know what a mimosa is?
-No.

09:10.591 --> 09:12.009
What is it? A snake?

09:12.927 --> 09:13.886
A viper?

09:15.763 --> 09:19.559
It's a very sensitive plant
that closes up when you touch it.

09:20.643 --> 09:24.730
I've decided to think of you as a mimosa.

09:25.648 --> 09:28.943
I'm going to be careful with you,
as if you're a mimosa.

09:30.194 --> 09:32.738
I'm not going to pressure you or anything.

09:33.281 --> 09:34.115
I promise you.

09:36.075 --> 09:39.287
You don't know anything about agriculture.

09:39.620 --> 09:41.080
Where did you learn about this?

09:41.998 --> 09:47.003
I can hold back and wait now.
Once you're ready to share a room...

09:47.878 --> 09:52.383
I mean, if you want to use
the same room again,

09:52.883 --> 09:53.759
give me a sign.

09:54.802 --> 09:55.970
Okay.

09:56.512 --> 09:57.430
Mimosa?

09:58.514 --> 09:59.348
Yes.

10:01.601 --> 10:02.435
Promise!

10:04.854 --> 10:05.730
Yes.

10:08.065 --> 10:08.899
Stamp.

10:11.569 --> 10:13.696
-Sign.
-No need to sign...

10:13.779 --> 10:14.739
Photocopy.

10:15.698 --> 10:16.657
Laminate.

10:18.326 --> 10:20.369
-Should we write this down?
-No.

10:32.506 --> 10:33.758
I'm so cool.

10:34.425 --> 10:35.843
So dependable!

10:36.844 --> 10:39.597
Wow, I'm so damn considerate.

10:40.389 --> 10:43.309
How? How did I come up with this?

10:44.560 --> 10:45.686
Hey, So-joon.

10:46.729 --> 10:49.649
Good manners make the man.

10:55.446 --> 10:56.405
What is this?

10:58.115 --> 11:00.159
If we made up,
we should use the same room.

11:01.243 --> 11:02.411
This is ridiculous.

11:06.165 --> 11:07.124
What was it?

11:08.542 --> 11:09.794
What is this mimosa?

11:10.294 --> 11:12.505
Where did this mimosa suddenly come from?

11:13.798 --> 11:14.757
Mimosa.

11:16.092 --> 11:19.637
<i>Mimosa flower means sensitive heart.</i>

11:20.054 --> 11:23.099
<i>When it is touched,</i>
<i>it acts like it is shy.</i>

11:23.182 --> 11:24.850
It should like being touched!

11:25.101 --> 11:26.769
It's just a measly weed.

11:27.687 --> 11:29.605
Teacher, you know the game.

11:29.730 --> 11:32.066
Can't you feel and see it?

11:32.149 --> 11:34.026
I can feel it and see it.

11:34.235 --> 11:36.737
This place is empty
and looks so common now.

11:36.821 --> 11:38.823
But it will turn into gold.

11:39.490 --> 11:40.866
I can guarantee it.

11:41.117 --> 11:44.203
Almost all of my investors are positive
about this.

11:44.286 --> 11:46.247
You need to make your move.

11:46.330 --> 11:48.874
Then we can start getting this land.
It is possible.

11:49.917 --> 11:50.751
Well...

11:52.753 --> 11:54.630
-I thought about it.
-Yes, Teacher.

11:56.424 --> 11:57.842
Leave your company now.

11:58.217 --> 12:02.596
-Then I will just...
-No, I told you before.

12:02.680 --> 12:04.223
-No.
-Leaving the company--

12:04.306 --> 12:08.269
I thought about it. Why would I invest
in something that's not upfront.

12:08.394 --> 12:09.228
Why?

12:09.478 --> 12:12.106
I don't need this. I don't need it at all.

12:16.444 --> 12:18.946
-Teacher, honestly...
-Yes.

12:19.822 --> 12:23.409
I don't know why you're helping me

12:24.577 --> 12:27.288
to start my own business,
pushing me forward.

12:28.873 --> 12:32.626
-Can I ask you why?
-I want to give you an opportunity.

12:34.170 --> 12:35.129
-An opportunity?
-Yes.

12:36.589 --> 12:38.758
Director Kim, you're ambitious.
Do you work out?

12:39.550 --> 12:42.887
I will help you grow and succeed.

12:47.266 --> 12:49.769
You almost sound like a shaman.

12:50.895 --> 12:54.023
I do have some foresight.
Let me take a look at you.

12:54.940 --> 12:57.359
Wow, Director Kim.

12:58.068 --> 13:00.529
I'm your last opportunity, Director Kim.

13:02.740 --> 13:03.574
Also, here.

13:04.617 --> 13:06.243
I brought my contract deposit.

13:06.327 --> 13:08.537
It's cash and certified checks,
1 billion won.

13:08.662 --> 13:11.665
-Excuse me?
-Oh yeah.Â That bag was too small.

13:11.749 --> 13:13.793
This is the rest. It wouldn't fit.

13:15.336 --> 13:17.505
I don't like to use banks.

13:18.380 --> 13:23.719
Would I scam you
when I'm giving you my money?

13:24.303 --> 13:26.931
I'll give the remaining 9 billion won
later when we sign.

13:27.515 --> 13:28.933
I have one condition.

13:29.767 --> 13:32.978
Once the land contract is processed,

13:33.229 --> 13:34.688
you leave Myreits.

13:35.189 --> 13:36.106
That's it.

13:37.942 --> 13:38.901
What do you think?

13:39.902 --> 13:41.946
Are you going down with the bag,

13:42.863 --> 13:44.406
or empty-handed?

13:47.743 --> 13:49.620
-I'm not doing it.
-No.

13:49.703 --> 13:52.706
No, Teacher.

13:53.249 --> 13:54.124
Well...

13:56.752 --> 13:58.546
Thank you so much for the opportunity.

14:00.172 --> 14:01.215
I will work hard.

14:06.428 --> 14:07.304
Opportunity?

14:08.264 --> 14:10.474
Giving me an opportunity? What a joke.

14:12.935 --> 14:15.521
Then are you moving forward with Jangho?

14:15.604 --> 14:18.315
Yes, the real game starts now.

14:18.399 --> 14:21.068
You need to focus now
and watch what you say.

14:21.569 --> 14:23.070
Of course, Director.

14:23.195 --> 14:24.071
I will do my best.

14:28.576 --> 14:29.535
Yu So-joon.

14:30.703 --> 14:31.662
Yu So-joon.

14:32.496 --> 14:35.749
You've had enough of your share,
you young punk.

14:36.625 --> 14:37.960
You can stop now.

14:38.502 --> 14:39.628
It's my turn.

15:09.033 --> 15:11.160
I have to look good

15:11.243 --> 15:13.537
for my mimosa.

15:13.621 --> 15:14.747
That's right.

15:25.925 --> 15:27.217
I feel bad now.

15:35.726 --> 15:37.561
<i>Flower, are you still sleeping?</i>

15:42.274 --> 15:45.569
<i>Yeah, Flower is getting up now.</i>

15:46.445 --> 15:47.780
<i>Gosh, I'm sleepy.</i>

15:53.452 --> 15:55.079
You're dead now.

15:57.623 --> 16:00.626
-Good morning, Realtor.
-Hi.

16:02.711 --> 16:03.671
What are you doing?

16:04.213 --> 16:06.757
Are you getting ready for work?

16:08.092 --> 16:11.470
Oh! I usually dress like this at home.

16:12.638 --> 16:15.933
You do?
But it'll be hard to exercise in that.

16:17.142 --> 16:18.018
Exercise?

16:20.187 --> 16:21.146
What exercise?

16:21.897 --> 16:24.400
Let's go jogging. Get changed first.

16:24.733 --> 16:27.111
No, I don't like to exercise.

16:27.945 --> 16:29.822
I only do it once or twice a year.

16:29.905 --> 16:31.865
One of those days is today.

16:31.949 --> 16:34.243
-Get changed.
-Then let's think of an exercise

16:34.952 --> 16:37.079
we could do at home instead of outside.

16:37.413 --> 16:38.288
At home?

16:39.832 --> 16:41.583
I'd like to do that too,

16:41.667 --> 16:43.836
but jogging is best outside.

16:43.919 --> 16:45.087
Go get changed.

16:47.006 --> 16:48.132
Go on.

16:48.215 --> 16:51.176
One, two...

16:54.722 --> 16:56.682
Your doctor says you need to get more fit.

16:57.307 --> 16:59.143
We should exercise every morning.

16:59.226 --> 17:00.185
Sounds good, right?

17:00.269 --> 17:03.480
I thought you don't like to exercise.

17:04.189 --> 17:05.858
-Yeah.
-You never exercise.

17:06.358 --> 17:08.193
I'll try hard, now.

17:08.610 --> 17:09.611
It's good!

17:11.488 --> 17:13.782
That's good and all.

17:14.575 --> 17:16.702
It's not good for people
to change so suddenly.

17:17.202 --> 17:20.956
Why do you think there's a saying,
"people die if they change too suddenly?"

17:23.876 --> 17:28.255
Can't we just live a long and simple life?

17:28.922 --> 17:32.551
I like you the way you are.

17:33.010 --> 17:34.845
If you have the strength to talk, run!

17:34.928 --> 17:35.888
Focus!

17:37.931 --> 17:39.183
I don't know.

17:39.475 --> 17:41.393
Don't use all your energy for running!

17:42.436 --> 17:45.355
Breathe.

17:46.440 --> 17:48.442
Do you think this is really what I want?

17:50.027 --> 17:51.028
Don't you like this?

17:54.490 --> 17:57.743
Maybe he doesn't feel
a sexual desire for you.

17:59.203 --> 18:01.163
He's so good to me,
I don't think that's it.

18:02.956 --> 18:04.291
Hello.

18:04.374 --> 18:06.418
-Hello.
-Hello! You're all here?

18:06.960 --> 18:10.714
-Kids, go in and practice your drills.
-Okay.

18:10.798 --> 18:12.466
I'll be in soon.

18:13.008 --> 18:13.884
Good.

18:16.678 --> 18:19.056
When you're a newlywed,

18:20.099 --> 18:23.268
I heard you do it in during meals
and in the middle of the night.

18:23.477 --> 18:25.104
While running the washing machine--

18:26.188 --> 18:28.273
Can't you hear
the innocent children playing?

18:29.274 --> 18:32.444
So do you think newlyweds
are slaves to lust?

18:33.362 --> 18:34.822
You watch too many weird things.

18:34.905 --> 18:36.698
Don't watch any more porn.

18:36.865 --> 18:39.743
No, friends of mine
who got married were like that.

18:40.202 --> 18:43.497
They said they could barely rest.

18:43.831 --> 18:45.791
Whether it was day or night,

18:45.874 --> 18:47.960
they would just look at each other.

18:48.043 --> 18:49.795
They would look away, then look again.

18:49.878 --> 18:51.505
Every time their eyes met,

18:51.588 --> 18:54.466
they would do it so hard
that their noses bled.

18:54.550 --> 18:57.594
-It was just crazy.
-Stop it.

18:58.929 --> 19:02.432
You look so conservative,
but you get so excited about this stuff.

19:02.891 --> 19:04.768
It's because I'm lonely.

19:06.019 --> 19:06.937
I'm lonely too.

19:08.272 --> 19:09.189
Very lonely.

19:13.527 --> 19:14.695
I don't need a lot.

19:15.237 --> 19:17.156
I just want to be in the same bed
with him.

19:17.281 --> 19:18.824
Just be honest with him.

19:19.783 --> 19:21.952
Do you need to hold back
because you're a woman?

19:22.578 --> 19:24.413
It's not an issue about women and men.

19:25.330 --> 19:29.418
Realtor has suddenly become very pure.

19:30.294 --> 19:32.129
Very pure and sincere.

19:33.505 --> 19:37.676
He's like a freshly ironed white shirt.

19:38.510 --> 19:40.137
I feel like I can't get dirt on it.

19:40.762 --> 19:42.514
I shouldn't touch it either.

19:43.140 --> 19:44.975
I feel like I'm some staining material.

19:47.394 --> 19:50.981
Anyway, I feel very awkward
to approach him first.

19:51.857 --> 19:53.192
I did rebuff him a lot, too.

19:54.526 --> 19:56.945
People often use separate rooms
and are comfortable.

19:57.029 --> 20:00.157
Apparently, many couples
use separate rooms forever.

20:00.574 --> 20:01.408
Really?

20:01.533 --> 20:04.036
So if you feel weird

20:04.119 --> 20:07.956
being all blatant towards him,

20:08.957 --> 20:11.126
just be subtle.

20:12.628 --> 20:13.921
Seduce him.

20:14.963 --> 20:16.506
How can I be subtle about it?

20:18.425 --> 20:19.551
Manager Shin.

20:20.385 --> 20:21.511
Wait.

20:22.846 --> 20:24.348
Well...

20:25.766 --> 20:28.769
About what you said yesterday,
did you mean it?

20:29.436 --> 20:30.312
Are you really...

20:31.939 --> 20:33.315
going to quit?

20:34.816 --> 20:37.236
Yes. Keep it to yourself for now.

20:44.076 --> 20:47.412
It seems like you haven't been in touch
with Se-young lately.

20:48.080 --> 20:49.998
I saw her at Happiness' house opening.

20:51.750 --> 20:54.002
You haven't met her separately, right?

20:54.544 --> 20:55.420
Hey, Kang Ki-doong.

20:56.338 --> 20:57.172
Yes?

20:57.714 --> 21:01.051
If you feigned innocence,
did you think I wouldn't know?

21:02.261 --> 21:04.137
When did I feign innocence?

21:05.305 --> 21:07.933
You pretended not to care, but...

21:09.142 --> 21:10.394
your heart couldn't resist?

21:12.771 --> 21:13.814
What?

21:15.732 --> 21:16.942
So, you do have feelings.

21:19.152 --> 21:21.530
Stop saying that nonsense.

21:22.155 --> 21:24.616
No matter what, she's a friend.
How could--

21:24.700 --> 21:27.160
Still, you shouldn't have touched
my babies.

21:27.869 --> 21:28.704
Babies?

21:29.037 --> 21:30.831
Take them off while I'm asking nicely.

21:31.832 --> 21:35.210
Take your dirty feet
out of my sacred sneakers.

21:35.294 --> 21:36.878
They're just shoes.

21:36.962 --> 21:39.047
Do you think they're made for wearing?

21:39.756 --> 21:41.341
I've never worn them myself.

21:41.675 --> 21:44.761
I went to the other world many times
just to get a pair.

21:44.845 --> 21:45.721
You're so petty.

21:45.804 --> 21:48.390
-I won't get them dirty.
-You're not taking them off?

21:49.099 --> 21:50.350
Come on.

21:51.393 --> 21:52.352
You're really not?

21:52.436 --> 21:54.855
I'll keep them clean, so don't worry.

21:55.188 --> 21:57.024
What are you doing? What!

21:57.107 --> 21:58.567
That hurts. My back hurts!

21:58.650 --> 22:00.777
My back hurts. Ouch! Hey!

22:00.861 --> 22:04.197
-Take them off.
-Hey, hey!

22:04.281 --> 22:06.825
-They're mine.
-Okay. All right.

22:10.412 --> 22:14.041
If you're going to come in
right after you knock,

22:14.124 --> 22:15.792
why bother knocking at all?

22:15.959 --> 22:19.046
You should wait at least three seconds
for a response.

22:19.463 --> 22:21.381
I... I'm sorry.

22:22.132 --> 22:24.176
