41:46.629 --> 41:48.088
Thanks so much.

41:48.714 --> 41:49.757
I love you.

41:49.840 --> 41:52.384
You must be so glad
to have a friend like me.

41:52.468 --> 41:54.720
You need to be grateful to me forever.

41:55.054 --> 41:56.263
I'll see how you do first.

41:56.722 --> 41:59.808
-Where are you going?
-To see how you did on your assignment.

42:00.017 --> 42:02.144
I'm going to get the files
from the other world.

42:02.228 --> 42:04.688
Gosh, that's so complicated.
Get out of here.

42:04.772 --> 42:08.275
I'm going to think
about time and space for a while.

42:08.859 --> 42:10.945
Your brain can't handle it.
Just accept it.

42:12.321 --> 42:15.407
Se-young said
she's going to work in Japan.

42:15.491 --> 42:16.909
-Have you heard?
-What?

42:16.992 --> 42:19.495
I met her earlier
and she suddenly said that.

42:20.955 --> 42:22.706
You should call her later.

42:22.790 --> 42:24.708
We should do a goodbye party or trip.

42:24.792 --> 42:27.378
Let's set something up.
We can't just send her off.

42:28.837 --> 42:31.715
Put all the files in the Flower folder,
okay?

42:47.523 --> 42:48.899
SHIN SE-YOUNG

42:55.030 --> 42:55.990
I'm not picking up.

42:57.700 --> 42:58.784
This one looks good.

42:59.285 --> 43:00.202
Try it on.

43:02.037 --> 43:04.790
This is Yu So-joon's style.
It looks like kids' shoes.

43:05.666 --> 43:07.418
Do you have to bring up Yu So-joon?

43:07.751 --> 43:09.545
I'm out here buying you shoes!

43:09.628 --> 43:11.130
I said I don't want it.

43:11.213 --> 43:12.798
Why are you buying me a pair?

43:13.132 --> 43:16.010
Did you hear something from So-joon?
That I took his sneakers?

43:16.093 --> 43:18.262
Stop bringing up Yu So-joon.

43:19.388 --> 43:21.515
I don't like seeing you wear
those old ones.

43:21.849 --> 43:24.059
Do you think I'm buying them
because I like you?

43:24.476 --> 43:25.853
I don't want to buy them now.

43:25.936 --> 43:28.272
What's wrong with mine?
What? What's so old?

43:28.355 --> 43:30.524
Stop complaining and choose a pair.

43:30.608 --> 43:34.028
Here we go. These ones.
These are Kang Ki-doong style.

43:35.237 --> 43:36.447
Are you blind?

43:37.531 --> 43:38.365
I don't want any.

43:40.492 --> 43:42.578
-Kang Ki-doong, come back.
-I don't want them.

43:42.661 --> 43:44.455
Come back before I count to three.

43:44.622 --> 43:46.707
One, two...

43:48.042 --> 43:49.251
I'm here. What now?

43:49.335 --> 43:52.713
I think the ones I chose are
the most stylish.

43:52.796 --> 43:54.214
Just get the ones I picked.

43:54.882 --> 43:56.050
They're the best ones.

43:57.134 --> 43:58.677
Whatever. Do what you want.

43:58.802 --> 44:00.054
I'm not thankful at all.

44:01.680 --> 44:04.058
I'm not thankful at all, but thanks.

44:04.391 --> 44:05.392
I'll wear them well.

44:06.685 --> 44:09.146
I'm getting insulted
even after buying them for you.

44:10.648 --> 44:12.358
Forget it. Let's go eat.

44:12.441 --> 44:14.234
No, I want to go.Â See you next time.

44:14.318 --> 44:16.236
You're not even going to buy me a meal?

44:16.320 --> 44:18.030
Didn't you buy me these
to get lost?

44:19.073 --> 44:22.368
If you were going to tell me about Japan
over dinner, forget it.

44:23.160 --> 44:24.620
I already know.

44:25.829 --> 44:27.206
I heard from So-joon.

44:32.711 --> 44:34.254
Then why didn't you say anything?

44:35.673 --> 44:38.634
It seems like
you keep making angry remarks.

44:38.717 --> 44:41.303
This is a goodbye present, right?

44:42.388 --> 44:45.099
-It is, right?
-It is. So, what?

44:45.182 --> 44:46.225
So, thanks.

44:46.308 --> 44:48.686
I'll make good use of them.
You're great. Good luck.

44:48.977 --> 44:50.813
I don't know
why you're taking that tone.

44:51.230 --> 44:52.773
Why are you getting mad at me?

44:52.856 --> 44:55.025
What did I do?

44:56.068 --> 44:57.778
I said thank you!

44:58.445 --> 44:59.905
I said farewell.

45:00.447 --> 45:02.491
Thank you and goodbye!

45:04.952 --> 45:08.455
Am I supposed to get emotional
because you bought me shoes?

45:31.019 --> 45:31.854
What is this?

45:32.604 --> 45:33.981
Why is it only up to October?

45:34.398 --> 45:35.899
Kang Ki-doong.

45:36.358 --> 45:38.110
He stopped after a few days?

45:41.155 --> 45:42.531
I should take this for now.

45:55.002 --> 45:58.964
They say your future is in your hands.
Literally, in this case.

46:08.849 --> 46:09.683
Flower.

46:10.225 --> 46:12.019
Should I buy some red bean bread?

46:14.146 --> 46:15.189
Hello?

46:15.939 --> 46:16.940
Anyone here?

46:18.525 --> 46:19.651
Is no one here?

46:31.872 --> 46:33.707
Oh, Ma-rin.

46:34.792 --> 46:35.959
What brings you here?

46:39.129 --> 46:40.047
You're...

46:41.381 --> 46:43.258
not the Yu So-joon that I know, are you?

46:49.389 --> 46:50.849
You're from the past.

46:54.728 --> 46:58.106
You... found out everything.

46:59.399 --> 47:00.275
I know it all.

47:01.693 --> 47:03.362
I know you're a time traveler.

47:04.655 --> 47:05.614
Yes.

47:06.949 --> 47:08.283
You must have been surprised.

47:11.161 --> 47:12.871
You're being very cold to me.

47:21.588 --> 47:24.258
Did I make you this way?

47:26.093 --> 47:29.513
Why did things go wrong for us?

47:30.514 --> 47:31.849
What other reasons are there?

47:33.350 --> 47:35.978
-Our feelings faded.
-I shouldn't have asked.

47:36.353 --> 47:37.521
I'm not curious at all.

47:41.358 --> 47:42.860
Your future will change too.

47:43.735 --> 47:45.028
When you wake up,

47:45.195 --> 47:49.366
I will be by your side,
as if nothing happened.

47:50.868 --> 47:53.620
You won't even remember

47:53.704 --> 47:55.289
meeting me here.

47:57.082 --> 48:00.586
You hating me won't have ever happened.

48:00.669 --> 48:01.837
Are you still doing that?

48:05.465 --> 48:07.718
We never should have met.

48:09.553 --> 48:10.596
You and I...

48:12.598 --> 48:14.391
were never meant to meet.

48:14.808 --> 48:17.019
You forcefully changed the future.

48:19.271 --> 48:20.564
That's why this happened.

48:22.024 --> 48:23.317
How much do you know?

48:24.401 --> 48:25.569
Once you return...

48:26.862 --> 48:28.947
end things with me as soon as you can.

48:30.574 --> 48:34.286
Put my life back the way it was.

48:36.997 --> 48:37.956
I don't want to.

48:44.046 --> 48:44.963
I like you.

48:49.426 --> 48:52.554
I'm scared that you'll change like this.

48:54.556 --> 48:58.018
So I've been so careful around you lately.

48:59.686 --> 49:02.856
I'm worried that you'll hate me.

49:04.024 --> 49:04.900
No,

49:06.318 --> 49:07.819
I'm worried that you'll get hurt.

49:09.237 --> 49:11.698
I'm just careful about everything.

49:13.659 --> 49:14.576
Yet stillâ¦

49:16.828 --> 49:17.704
I'm happy.

49:21.083 --> 49:23.210
I certainly like you.

49:23.919 --> 49:26.254
And I will certainly continue to like you.

49:28.924 --> 49:31.802
You're talking
as if you don't remember any of it.

49:33.595 --> 49:35.222
That's why I'm telling you this.

49:36.640 --> 49:37.557
I remember.

49:43.355 --> 49:44.982
Even though it was brief.

49:48.360 --> 49:49.528
That moment...

49:51.363 --> 49:53.031
is everything to me right now.

50:03.709 --> 50:07.462
Has Se-young not left for Japan yet?

50:09.923 --> 50:13.010
If she hasn't left for Japan yet,
don't let Se-young leave.

50:15.387 --> 50:16.638
That's all I have to say.

50:45.584 --> 50:47.002
<i>I'm not in Seoul right now.</i>

50:47.294 --> 50:49.046
<i>Can you come pick me up?</i>

50:49.129 --> 50:51.840
<i>I'm waiting. Call me when you get this.</i>

50:54.509 --> 50:56.178
Where are you? Is something wrong?

51:08.440 --> 51:10.609
Ma-rin, are you okay?

51:10.984 --> 51:12.152
Are you hurt?

51:12.235 --> 51:13.445
I was waiting for you.

51:13.528 --> 51:14.613
Come sit.

51:16.698 --> 51:19.743
Gosh! You scared me.

51:19.826 --> 51:22.621
I made a little fire to set the mood.

51:23.246 --> 51:24.081
Hurry up.

51:24.289 --> 51:26.458
Are you shooting a horror film
or something?

51:26.541 --> 51:28.919
What kind of mood can we have
at a construction site?

51:29.002 --> 51:32.464
-You have to come here every time?
-But it's nice, isn't it?

51:33.131 --> 51:34.800
Were you here alone?

51:36.635 --> 51:38.845
What kind of girl stays here alone
so fearlessly?

51:39.679 --> 51:43.308
This complex is being built thanks to you.

51:46.353 --> 51:48.396
I wanted you to see it
when no one is around.

51:49.147 --> 51:51.108
A lot of your effort has gone into it.

51:53.026 --> 51:56.113
You wouldn't have come
unless I did something like this.

51:56.196 --> 51:57.489
So I played a little trick.

51:58.281 --> 52:00.617
I even refused a ride
from the board director.

52:03.995 --> 52:07.332
Still, you shouldn't be
at a construction site alone.

52:07.833 --> 52:09.793
Stop lecturing me.

52:10.127 --> 52:11.294
It's so nice here.

52:14.256 --> 52:16.258
I'm relieved nothing happened to you.

52:18.552 --> 52:21.346
Then will you be taking pictures here?

52:22.472 --> 52:23.348
Yes.

52:24.266 --> 52:27.352
I'll be keeping
a record of them building this.

52:28.270 --> 52:30.147
They'll use it for promotional purposes.

52:30.564 --> 52:32.816
There's a photo exhibition
at the end of the year.

52:35.569 --> 52:38.280
I guess you're officially going to work
at Happiness.

52:40.073 --> 52:44.035
Yeah, there will be many opportunities
to take good pictures,

52:44.744 --> 52:46.413
and it's something important to you.

52:47.247 --> 52:48.874
It's also a family business.

52:49.749 --> 52:53.044
Aren't I being a good daughter-in-law
to the Yu family?

52:57.090 --> 52:59.467
Here you go.Â Oh, it's hot.

52:59.551 --> 53:00.510
What is it?

53:01.011 --> 53:01.970
I...

53:03.930 --> 53:05.473
prepared this for you.

53:05.557 --> 53:07.100
-It's so hot.
-Here. I'll do it.

53:07.184 --> 53:08.268
No, no.

53:08.602 --> 53:11.938
You'll get soot on your hands.
I'll peel it for you to eat.

53:13.523 --> 53:14.357
Here.

53:16.985 --> 53:18.403
It looks good, right?

53:20.363 --> 53:22.073
You've never roasted potatoes, right?

53:24.576 --> 53:27.037
-Isn't this a sweet potato?
-No, it's a potato.

53:27.579 --> 53:28.413
Oh, it is.

53:29.456 --> 53:30.665
It looks good, doesn't it?

53:30.749 --> 53:32.500
-Can I eat it?
-Yes. Try it.

53:36.046 --> 53:37.631
Be careful. It's hot.

53:44.012 --> 53:45.805
-Is it good?
-No.

53:48.642 --> 53:49.851
What was that?

53:50.852 --> 53:52.979
-It's good, right?
-It is.

53:54.564 --> 53:57.359
Did you take any pictures today?

53:57.734 --> 53:59.444
Show me if you did.

53:59.903 --> 54:03.240
Today, I spent my time gettingÂ friendly
with the construction crew.

54:04.449 --> 54:06.159
Look at the ones
from the 30th house?

54:07.035 --> 54:09.788
Everyone loved
how the pictures turned out.

54:10.956 --> 54:12.999
My talent is just exploding.

54:13.583 --> 54:14.459
Take a look.

54:18.046 --> 54:20.048
I'm relieved that everyone liked them.

54:20.507 --> 54:21.967
Start from here.

54:33.895 --> 54:35.230
Are you touched by that one?

54:35.981 --> 54:38.441
Be quiet. I'm looking.

54:43.363 --> 54:45.365
I hope we can grow old together like them.

54:50.078 --> 54:51.079
What?

54:53.748 --> 54:55.458
I was just thinking the same thing.

55:00.171 --> 55:02.507
Marriage is really amazing.

55:04.968 --> 55:08.555
We didn't really know each other
just a few months ago.

55:10.765 --> 55:11.725
Now,

55:13.101 --> 55:15.770
we're planning out
the rest of our lives together.

55:19.691 --> 55:23.611
Even when I'm an old grandma,
you will be there with me.

55:24.195 --> 55:25.864
I think that's so amazing.

55:30.744 --> 55:31.661
I know.

55:32.412 --> 55:34.831
You and I were never meant to meet.

55:36.374 --> 55:37.417
<i>Once you return,</i>

55:38.335 --> 55:40.378
end things with me as soon as you can.

55:40.837 --> 55:44.341
Put my life back the way it was.

55:46.926 --> 55:49.054
What do you think we'll be like
when we're old?

55:49.971 --> 55:52.098
I wish I had a time machine
to see for myself.

55:56.144 --> 55:56.978
Realtor.

55:57.854 --> 56:01.024
What would you want to do
if you could go to the future?

56:01.858 --> 56:02.692
Stocks?

56:03.860 --> 56:04.986
Lottery?

56:07.530 --> 56:10.116
You could see
what land will increase in value.

56:10.700 --> 56:12.327
That is your job.

56:13.536 --> 56:14.496
Hold on.

56:14.579 --> 56:15.538
Why?

56:17.290 --> 56:18.541
Do I have soot on my face?

56:18.958 --> 56:19.793
Yes.

56:20.794 --> 56:22.170
Here? Here too?

56:30.095 --> 56:32.305
I'm not the type
to get stuff on my face.

56:32.722 --> 56:34.099
Maybe it's on my hands.

56:35.809 --> 56:36.810
Am I really dirty?

56:37.894 --> 56:40.355
No. You're so pretty.

56:41.356 --> 56:42.273
You're cute.

56:46.403 --> 56:48.613
I wish every day was like today.

56:52.367 --> 56:53.368
Me too.

56:57.831 --> 56:59.499
Oh, that looks good.

57:02.585 --> 57:05.922
Cooking is so easy
when the kitchen is this big.

57:09.634 --> 57:11.177
It was good today, right?

57:11.553 --> 57:12.470
It was.

57:13.138 --> 57:14.139
-Oh, my!
-What!

57:14.222 --> 57:16.057
Why would you get scared
seeing your mom?

57:16.266 --> 57:18.643
Oh, my son!

57:18.726 --> 57:20.061
You're coming home now?

57:20.145 --> 57:21.020
Hello, Mother!

57:21.688 --> 57:24.107
How did you get in?
How did you get a key?

57:24.190 --> 57:27.026
My son gave me one last time.

57:28.027 --> 57:30.613
My son wanted me to come
whenever I want to.

57:30.738 --> 57:32.240
I gave her one.
I did good, right?

57:33.116 --> 57:35.410
You must be hungry. I cooked for you.

57:35.535 --> 57:37.662
-Oh, then I'll wash up.
-Okay.

57:39.122 --> 57:40.373
You cooked, Mom?

57:40.457 --> 57:42.041
I made what I'm good at.

57:42.125 --> 57:43.376
You must be crazy.

57:43.460 --> 57:45.128
The pork is really good.

57:45.670 --> 57:47.672
-I made soybean paste stew.
-Don't make that.

57:47.755 --> 57:50.383
-Well, then. There's mackerel.
-Don't do mackerel.

57:51.009 --> 57:52.427
-There's noodles.
-No noodles.

57:52.510 --> 57:53.845
I bought these.

57:54.679 --> 57:56.890
-This is the only store-bought?
-Yes. Taste it.

58:00.602 --> 58:04.147
I didn't prepare much,
but enjoy your meal, son.

58:04.230 --> 58:06.232
Mother, thank you for the food.

58:08.359 --> 58:09.194
You eat too.

58:11.988 --> 58:13.698
What is it? Is something wrong?

58:14.240 --> 58:16.117
No. It's just so good.

58:16.201 --> 58:17.494
You can be honest.

58:17.911 --> 58:19.579
My mom needs to know the truth.

58:21.414 --> 58:24.542
I see that Ma-rin learned
to cook from you.

58:24.626 --> 58:26.920
-My cooking is that good?
-My cooking is that bad?

58:28.213 --> 58:31.633
I meant that they were both good.

58:34.302 --> 58:35.386
You shouldn't...

58:38.890 --> 58:42.185
This stew is very unique and modern.

58:42.310 --> 58:45.230
It's like art. It's great.

58:46.648 --> 58:49.359
Just consider the thought put into it
and eat up.

58:49.442 --> 58:51.528
-Food is all about effort.
-Sure.

58:52.362 --> 58:54.948
Here, I will make a lettuce wrap.

58:57.075 --> 58:58.284
Oh, Mom.

58:58.952 --> 58:59.911
Yeah?

59:00.161 --> 59:03.665
-Did you say you're staying over?
-Huh? Did I?

59:08.503 --> 59:10.129
You said you were sleeping over.

59:11.130 --> 59:13.466
You should sleep here. It's late.

59:13.967 --> 59:15.260
There's a room upstairs.

59:15.343 --> 59:16.678
Should I do that?

59:17.178 --> 59:18.638
Something's up, right?

59:18.721 --> 59:20.306
There's nothing.

59:20.390 --> 59:23.101
It's late.Â Get some good sleep tonight.

59:23.184 --> 59:25.979
Something's going on.
Why won't you tell me?

59:26.229 --> 59:27.730
Am I supposed to live here, then?

59:27.897 --> 59:30.233
One day can turn into two.
Two can turn into a year.

59:30.650 --> 59:32.151
Why would you say such a thing?

59:32.694 --> 59:33.778
Go to bed.

59:33.861 --> 59:34.821
Sleep tight.

59:34.946 --> 59:37.865
So-joon is a light sleeper,
so don't come downstairs.

59:37.949 --> 59:39.325
What if I need the bathroom?

59:39.409 --> 59:41.661
Go to sleep. A bathroom is right there.

59:41.744 --> 59:43.162
-Okay.
-Bye.

59:43.288 --> 59:44.247
Good night.

59:44.330 --> 59:45.790
Good night.

59:47.959 --> 59:48.876
Gosh.

59:49.502 --> 59:52.171
This is nice and soft.

59:52.255 --> 59:54.007
Oh so good!

59:54.591 --> 59:55.550
Oh my.

59:56.676 --> 59:59.429
Thanks to my daughter,
I get to sleep on this nice bed.

1:00:37.592 --> 1:00:39.260
We became her parents,

1:00:40.178 --> 1:00:41.763
and never did anything for her.

1:00:43.097 --> 1:00:45.475
All we did was cause her suffering.

1:00:50.104 --> 1:00:53.941
Your daughter is living
in this big house now.

1:00:55.443 --> 1:00:58.613
She wasn't blessed with good parents,
just a good husband.

1:01:07.413 --> 1:01:08.247
Realtor.

1:01:08.748 --> 1:01:10.041
Wait a second.

1:01:12.251 --> 1:01:14.545
-You're going to sleep in there?
-What?

1:01:16.381 --> 1:01:17.715
My mom is here.

1:01:18.966 --> 1:01:20.259
Oh, right.

1:01:20.760 --> 1:01:22.053
If we use separate rooms...

1:01:22.470 --> 1:01:24.889
She'll worry and think we're fighting.

1:01:25.890 --> 1:01:29.936
A lifestyle like ours is not common.

1:01:30.937 --> 1:01:32.855
It won't be easy to understand.

1:01:34.190 --> 1:01:35.066
Then...

1:01:35.149 --> 1:01:36.192
What else?

1:01:36.776 --> 1:01:39.987
We need to pretend to use one room
while my mom is here.

1:01:41.864 --> 1:01:42.907
Should we?

1:01:43.157 --> 1:01:45.743
I guess we have no choice, right?

1:01:45.827 --> 1:01:46.994
We have no choice.

1:01:47.078 --> 1:01:48.037
Yes.

1:01:48.996 --> 1:01:49.872
Okay.

1:02:24.031 --> 1:02:26.367
Good night, Mimosa.

1:02:30.037 --> 1:02:30.997
You too.

1:03:04.071 --> 1:03:05.406
What, what?

1:03:06.866 --> 1:03:08.075
I'm so thirsty.

1:03:08.326 --> 1:03:09.410
Should I get you water?

1:03:11.496 --> 1:03:12.330
No, thanks.

1:03:16.834 --> 1:03:18.211
So hot.

1:03:19.879 --> 1:03:21.255
I can get it for you.

1:03:24.550 --> 1:03:26.260
Where is the hula hoop?

1:03:33.142 --> 1:03:37.897
Must you be the one
wrapped around my waist tonight?

1:03:45.822 --> 1:03:47.114
What are you doing here?

1:03:49.075 --> 1:03:50.034
Can't you see?

1:03:50.701 --> 1:03:51.994
I'm doing the hula hoop.

1:03:52.662 --> 1:03:55.623
Why are you doing that so late?

1:03:55.706 --> 1:03:56.582
Leave me be.

1:03:57.959 --> 1:04:00.545
I'm overflowing with strength.
I'm so hot.

1:04:01.337 --> 1:04:03.381
Sleep tonight.
Tomorrow morning, we can--

1:04:03.464 --> 1:04:04.841
I don't like mornings.

1:04:05.049 --> 1:04:06.759
I'm a night person.

1:04:08.386 --> 1:04:09.554
Okay, then.

1:04:10.388 --> 1:04:11.472
Don't go overboard.

1:04:11.806 --> 1:04:13.975
They say too much
can harm your intestines.

1:04:14.809 --> 1:04:16.727
Ruin my intestines? Yeah, right.

1:04:17.228 --> 1:04:19.689
Hey! Yu So-joon.

1:04:19.772 --> 1:04:20.606
Yeah?

1:04:20.690 --> 1:04:22.441
Why are you so dull?

1:04:23.651 --> 1:04:26.070
How many more signs do I need to give you?

1:04:26.737 --> 1:04:30.867
You asked me for a sign
if I'm ready and open.

1:04:31.242 --> 1:04:32.743
Should I actually sign something?

1:04:33.870 --> 1:04:35.496
Bring a pen. I'll sign something.

1:04:35.913 --> 1:04:36.747
Okay.

1:04:43.671 --> 1:04:45.882
Look at this.
You're pretending to be innocent.

1:04:46.299 --> 1:04:48.551
Earlier, you kept touching me
and set the mood,

1:04:48.634 --> 1:04:50.970
when I didn't even have soot on my face.

1:04:51.304 --> 1:04:52.388
Are you teasing me?

1:04:53.723 --> 1:04:54.807
Did you feel teased?

1:04:55.308 --> 1:04:56.309
I didn't know.

1:04:58.394 --> 1:04:59.270
Don't smile.

1:05:01.147 --> 1:05:02.064
Then...

1:05:02.940 --> 1:05:06.027
you like me, right?

1:05:06.110 --> 1:05:08.946
Did I ever not like you?

1:05:09.947 --> 1:05:12.617
Did I act like you were a man
I didn't like?

1:05:13.034 --> 1:05:13.868
No.

1:05:15.036 --> 1:05:17.288
I just wanted to hear it
from you directly.

1:05:19.665 --> 1:05:20.541
I love you.

1:05:24.253 --> 1:05:26.380
As for that secret you can't tell me yet,

1:05:27.465 --> 1:05:29.008
I'm not curious at all anymore.

1:05:29.383 --> 1:05:31.886
I just love you, no matter what.

1:05:32.261 --> 1:05:33.596
I love you, Yu So-joon.

1:05:37.850 --> 1:05:38.851
You can have me.

1:05:40.269 --> 1:05:41.520
I want to have you too.

1:06:46.210 --> 1:06:49.338
<i>Will tomorrow be as happy as today?</i>

